Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人  难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得想给他一个早安的吻让他大吃一惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙竟然为了这么无聊的理由潜入我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是察觉到了我的存在  故意在搞笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然东西不多  但却凌乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服脱了就直接这样扔着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这件不是干净的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有股微妙的男人味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  我说不定挺喜欢这股味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  难道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还真跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我预测的一样  她跳到床上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的味道好浓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人的味道竟然让人如此欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别摇屁股啊  屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  不行  这么做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}不行  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}不行  忍住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我的推理无误的话  这家伙只是个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好色的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  这里不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  雄二…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你从什么时候开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很早之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…  等…  不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经嫁不出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别丧气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在把我的枕头放进股间摩擦之前回过神来不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有在安慰我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  莳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就快迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪天音姐一直躲在厕所里不肯出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才会变得这么晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都和你说了对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最不擅长跑步了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让我教你首让跑步变得快乐的美妙歌曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着我唱  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「周防天音好淫乱」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「周防天音好淫乱」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「在男人的床上滚来滚去」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「在男人的床上滚来滚去」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「Good for you」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「Good for you」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}喂  等等  这歌怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「Good for me」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「Good for me」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}啊  住口
